creating a rest api for the following end points (E-com website)
1. REGISTER A NEW USER (username , email, password, confirm password)
    in register controller checklist sre
    1.1 validate the request
    1.2 authorise the request
    1.3 check user is in the database already
    1.4 prepare schema and models
    1.5 store new user in database 
    1.6 generate jwt token
    1.7 send response
2. LOGIN USER
3. LOGED IN AUTORIZATION
4. ADD NEW PRODUCT
5. UPDATE A PRODUCT
6. GET ALL PRODUCT LIST
7. GET SINGLE PRODUCT
8. DELETE PRODUCT
